    - target: {fileID: 4453553695309046325, guid: 0b9f24e443a4f5c47b3574754a5fb454, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "You roam in and out of about a hundred thousand doors, in some imaginary,
        I'd like to think. The real world, meanwhile, spins quite quickly. I am tired
        these days; scrubbing already-dry batter off the kitchen walls and packing
        my life into brown boxes bound for California. The world spins quite quickly
        so I can\u2019t entertain these tauntings; I think you\u2019d blow me clean
        over. Misery and I both know he kicks hard in the shins and could render
        me useless for a week or two.  Though, I am still quite sure you taught me
        everything I know about love. Though, you still are something I can\u2019t
        quite remember."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
